The evidence with the title 'Walker is either lying or isn't to bright about Medicaid funding ... ' says Jan 4, 2015  ... In february , the governor was under fire for rejecting the federal Medicaid expansion . He said he didn't trust that the money would come. He said: "federal government reneging " on Medicaid payments to Wisconsin caused about $240 million in extra costs in the 2013-'15 state budget . 
